Roundout Heist Strikes Illinois Train#John Ortiz#Thieves struck a mail train in Roundout, Illinois. The thieves, a part of the Egan's Rats gang, attacked the train and stole large amounts of property and money. The robbery has been discovered to be an inside job, revealing just how far the Rats' influence stretches.
